Package: riesznet
Type: Package
Title: Neural-Network Riesz Regression
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alejandro", "Schuler", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alejandro.schuler@gmail.com")
Description: R wrapper around the Python 'riesznet' package — neural-network
    estimation of the Riesz representer of a linear functional. Trains a
    PyTorch model against the Bregman-Riesz loss. Sister package to
    'rieszboost', 'krrr', and 'forestriesz'. Reuses 'rieszreg' for estimand
    specification.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    R6,
    reticulate (>= 1.30),
    rieszreg (>= 0.0.1)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    pkgload
Config/testthat/edition: 3
